<view class="page">
  <view class="card">
    <view class="title">主动提问</view>
    <view class="status">
      当前状态：{{pageStatusText}}
    </view>

    <view class="info-block" wx:if="{{name}}">
      <view>当前学生：{{name}}</view>
      <view>学号：{{studentId}}</view>
    </view>

    <view class="tip">本节课主动提问申请：{{questionRequestCount}} / 3</view>
    <view class="tip" wx:if="{{latestQuestionStatusText}}">{{latestQuestionStatusText}}</view>
    <view class="tip" wx:elif="{{!signSuccess}}">
      请先进入当前课堂完成签到，再返回这里提交提问申请。
    </view>
    <view class="tip" wx:else>
      提交后，老师侧会沿用现有课堂互动链路处理你的提问申请。
    </view>

    <button
      class="submit-btn"
      type="primary"
      bindtap="submitQuestionRequest"
      disabled="{{!canSubmitQuestionRequest}}"
    >
      提交主动提问申请
    </button>
  </view>
</view>
